        "Description": [
          {
            "text": "Our Portable Travel Plastic Protector Toothbrush Head Cover Cap is crafted from high-quality, durable plastic, designed to be lightweight, transparent, and washable. Each cover withstands daily use, maintaining clarity and functionality while adding style to bathroom essentials. It provides a hygienic barrier, protecting bristles from dust, bacteria, and contaminants. Measuring 1.77x1.77x1.06 inches, it fits most manual and electric toothbrushes, suitable for home, camping, school, travel, gym, and work. The breathable design with air holes keeps the toothbrush clean and safe on the go. Ideal for promotional events, wholesale, or bulk orders, these customizable covers can be branded with logos, making them perfect for businesses, travel enthusiasts, kids, and adults. Protect your toothbrush in style wherever life takes you.",
            "type": "text"
          }
