        "完整描述": "Our travel toothbrush head covers are made of high-quality, durable plastic and are designed to be lightweight, transparent, and washable. Each cover is carefully crafted to withstand daily use while maintaining its clarity and functionality. Not only do they protect your toothbrush, but they also add a touch of style to your bathroom essentials. They are easy to use and provide a hygienic barrier between your toothbrush and the environment, protecting the bristles from dust, bacteria, and other contaminants. Each cover measures 1.77x 1.77 x 1.06 inches and fits most manual and electric toothbrushes. They are suitable for a variety of environments, including home, camping, school, travel, gym, and work. The breathable box allows you to keep your toothbrush clean and safe wherever you go.",
